code: public static void initialize() {     if (ClassUtils.isPresent("org.slf4j.impl.StaticLoggerBinder", null) && ClassUtils.isPresent("ch.qos.logback.classic.Logger", null)) {         new Initializer().setRootLogLevel().     } }
